hotels.title: Universal Cabana
hotels.description: Redefine family time with a stay in one of these affordable suites. From the two 40 TVs to the convenient kitchenette to the brilliant bathroom area – designed to let three people get ready at once – they give everyone more room to relax.

hotels.title: Barut Resort
hotels.description: This hotel fits in nicely between mountains and the Med. The thin strip of private beach comes with loungers and its very own pier. If you want shops, bars and restaurants, Kemer’s centre is about 10 minutes’ walk, away.

hotels.title: Limak Limra Resort
hotels.description: With a backdrop of the Taurus Mountains and located on extensive land, the marvellous hotel is beautifully situated directly on the beach of Kiriş, about 5 km away from the popular holiday resort of Kemer with its numerous shopping possibilities.

hotels.title: Elegance Hotel Kemer
hotels.description: Elegance Hotel Kemer has a seasonal outdoor swimming pool, garden, a shared lounge and private beach area in Kemer. Among the facilities of this property are a restaurant, a 24-hour front desk and room service, along with free WiFi. The accommodation features a hammam and evening entertainment.

hotels.title: Camyuva Beach Hotel
hotels.description: Just 200 m from its blue flag private beach, Camyuva Beach Hotel has an outdoor pool, spa facilities and free Wi-Fi. It offers air-conditioned rooms with a satellite TV and minibar.

hotels.title: DoubleTree By Hilton Antalya-Kemer
hotels.description: Featuring an outdoor pool and a beach, DoubleTree By Hilton Antalya-Kemer is located in the centre of Kemer. Guests can enjoy the beach club, eclectic programme of daily events and savour a wide range of delicacies at the 12 gourmet food trucks and mobile kitchens.

hotels.title: Meder Resort Hotel
hotels.description: Meder Resort Hotel in Kemer is situated 800 m from Mediterranean Sea. It offers spacious rooms and has a large outdoor pool with a sun-lounger terrace. Guests can enjoy the free WiFi at the lobby.

hotels.title: Pine House Hotel
hotels.description: Set in pine forests with views of the Mediterranean and Taurus Mountains, this hotel offers a private beach and large outdoor pool. The Olympos antique city is 15 km away.

hotels.title: Orange County Resort Hotel Kemer
hotels.description: Styled on Amsterdam’s 16th-century architecture, this modern all-inclusive property features a private beach along the Mediterranean and a private jetty. There are 3 outdoor pools and 1 indoor pool. Show cooking, organic Dutch cuisine and Ottoman delicacies are part of the dining offer.
